OL,3,CThree-year-old boy died after
OL,4,Cprocedure by hospital trainee, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FAn inquest has heard that a three-year-
OL,8,Fold boy died after a trainee doctor
OL,9,Faccidentally pierced a major artery
OL,10,Fduring a routine biopsy at Birmingham
OL,11,FChildren's Hospital.
OL,13,FAarav Chopra from Wolverhampton
OL,14,Fsuffered a cardiac arrest triggered by
OL,15,Fa build-up of blood in his chest
OL,16,Fcavity, and died on 22 November 2023.
OL,18,FAn inquest was told a trainee
OL,19,Fperformed a liver biopsy on Aarav, and
OL,20,Fpierced an artery with a needle.
