OL,3,CThree-year-old boy died after
OL,4,Cprocedure by hospital trainee, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe trainee was thought to be a year
OL,8,Fsix, but was only in the fourth year
OL,9,Fof his training.
OL,11,FAarav died as a result of serious
OL,12,Fbrain damage, as doctors spent nearly
OL,13,F30 minutes trying to resuscitate him.
OL,15,FMonths earlier he had undergone a
OL,16,Fliver transplant, and was later
OL,17,Fundergoing tests at Birmingham
OL,18,FChildren's Hospital when he had the
OL,19,Ffailed biopsy.
