OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FMrs Hunt called out "poor planning" by
OL,8,Fstaff before the biopsy as she called
OL,9,Fon Women's and Children's NHS
OL,10,FFoundation Trust to set out what
OL,11,Faction it would take.
OL,13,FIn her report, she said there was
OL,14,F"poor" communication about the bleed
OL,15,FAarav suffered, "all of which hampered
OL,16,Ftreatment after his collapse."
OL,18,FShe raised concerns an internal
OL,19,Fmeeting following Aarav's death found
OL,20,F"there was no immediate learning from
OL,21,Fthis tragedy."
