OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FHis parents were also unaware a
OL,8,Ftrainee would be performing the biopsy
OL,9,Fon their son.
OL,11,F"There is a void and emptiness in our
OL,12,Flives that will never be filled"
OL,14,FIn a joint statement, Aarav's parents
OL,15,FKishore and Amrita Chopra said: "Aarav
OL,16,Fwas the most courageous little boy.
OL,18,F"He was a happy soul with the most
OL,19,Fbeautiful smile and adorable laugh.
