OL,3,CThree-year-old boy died after
OL,4,Cprocedure by hospital trainee, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F"For over 12 months, we raised
OL,8,Fconcerns with the hospital about what
OL,9,Fwe believed was a lack of clarity and
OL,10,Ftransparency surrounding Aarav's
OL,11,Fdeath."
OL,13,F"We only learned about the involvement
OL,14,Fof a trainee doctor in Aarav's biopsy
OL,15,Fprocedure through a Teams video
OL,16,Frecording of a meeting held by the
OL,17,Fhospital to discuss Aarav's death in
OL,18,Fmore detail.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/13
