OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F376A1742815305
OL,3,CThree-year-old boy died after
OL,4,Cprocedure by hospital trainee, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F"The hospital provided this video nine
OL,8,Fmonths after his death, and this
OL,9,Fcrucial information was never
OL,10,Fdisclosed to us earlier.
OL,12,F"The coroner's inquest and subsequent
OL,13,Ffindings confirmed our fears about the
OL,14,Finadequate standard of care that Aarav
OL,15,Freceived.
OL,17,F"The inquest has vindicated our
OL,18,Fconcerns but has also deeply upset us.
OL,19,FThe hospital's lack of accountability
OL,20,Fhas completely shattered our trust."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/13
