OL,4,Cprocedure by hospital trainee, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe inquest heard Aarav went into
OL,8,Fcardiac arrest at 1:30pm after the
OL,9,Finitial procedure, and an ultrasound
OL,10,Fat 2pm confirmed a large build up of
OL,11,Fblood on his chest, but no drain was
OL,12,Finserted.
OL,14,FThe report said: "There was no joined
OL,15,Fup discussion about how to best treat
OL,16,FAarav and it was unclear who was
OL,17,Fleading decision making for the
OL,18,Fcomplication that had occurred."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/13
