OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FLater that afternoon Aarav was taken
OL,8,Fback to theatre where his punctured
OL,9,Fartery was treated.
OL,11,FDespite surgery he died two days later.
OL,13,FHis parents have now instructed
OL,14,Fmedical negligence lawyers to
OL,15,Finvestigate with a view to suing the
OL,16,Fhospital trust.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/13
