OL,7,FDr Satish Rao, Chief Medical Officer
OL,8,Fat Birmingham Women's and Children's
OL,9,FNHS Foundation Trust, said: "We offer
OL,10,Four sincere condolences to Aarav's
OL,11,Ffamily and loved ones.
OL,13,F"It's clear from the findings of this
OL,14,Finquest, along with those from an
OL,15,Finvestigation conducted by the Trust
OL,16,Flast year, that the standard of care
OL,17,Fprovided did not meet those expected
OL,18,Fand, for this, we are truly sorry.
